#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:6
msgid ""
"A slide's player to show slides (mostly as pictures) one page by "
"another. The default interval between two slides is 3 seconds."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Child Components"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:10
msgid ""
"It supports all kinds of weex components as its slides, especially the "
"`indicator` component which can be used only as a child component of "
"`slider`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:14
msgid ""
"- `auto-play`: &lt;boolean&gt; `true` | `false`. This value determines "
"whether the slides plays automatically after the page rendering "
"finished. The default value is `false`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex_doc/weex/doc/components/slider.md:16
msgid ""
"Other attributes please check out the [common "
"attributes](../references/common-attrs.md)."
msgstr ""

